<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">I don't think it has anything to do with being uptight. Yes it is a game but the same rules apply as in rl. If you are doing something or saying something that upsets people, what is the big deal about NOT saying it. It's enough that it upsets some people. So it doesn't bother you, that's great. But for those it does bother, why not refrain from saying it to make their day more pleasant. You don't have to agree with them or see their side, just accomodate those who dislike it by not using the term.<BR><BR>Tara</FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#e6ebd7"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=383"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of TaraForestChild"></a>
